main.name: Cleaner Austin
main.description: Our non-profit specializes in cleaning trash inhibiting the ecosystems in Austin. Austin has been a clean city for as long as we could remember. But recently trash has started to pile up on the sides of roads, buildings, and nature. Our goal is to remove as much trash as we can and restore Austin to its former beauty.
main.bio: We are a non-profit organization founded by Austin-area high school students in 2022. Our goal is to rally volunteers who are passionate about the city of Austin and help do our part to keep our city beautiful.
main.contactmessage: Questions or suggestions? Email us or submit the form below!
